item.title: Im having trouble!
item.dc:creator: @archerer98 Archer
item.description:
@archerer98 wrote:

You mean servers?

Download moparscape 3.2 client here http://moparisthebest.com/moparscape.html . Then once thats installed open it up and type in a username and pass and for the ip go to the “help” tab at the top and click “server status” and pick a server thats on that you want to play,then type the ip of that server where it asks for the ip on moparscape and click login.The server status page is only about 50-75% accurate so it might say the server is on on the server
status page when its really not,you just have to keep trying till you get in.For more server status pages go to
www.dodian.com or www.rs-server.net
